cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.HC 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and sentence compression. The use of eye-tracking corpora and multi-layer LSTMs also suggests a possible fit with cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). The use of machine learning algorithms and multi-task learning also suggests a possible fit with cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
